args: After that, I continued my travels through\nall the worlds before arriving at this one.
Why have you come here? If you knew\nthe powers you were trifling with...
I've no time to bandy about words.\nI will stop you from forging this\ndragonpact, no matter the cost!
I had begun to suspect this world was\nsomething of an anomaly. But in that\nmoment, I knew it for true.
I will right this twisted world and reforge\nit into the one it was meant to be!
You are wrong. Stop this madness...\nNo right can come of...such suffering...
Aaah ha ha! What do you think you can do,\nbroken and powerless as you are?
But I have power enough left\nto send them far from here!
Forgive me. My journey ends in failure;\nI was unable to avert a future of misery.
But next time... If I might be granted just\none more chance...
Etch these words into your heart, Brother,\nfor there will come a time when you\nmust decide.
Do not worry about my life.\nSeek the Dawnshard for your own.
With the power of the Other restored,\nmy channel was severed.
In all the worlds I'd visited, that had never\nhappened. Frankly, it baffled me.
But it DID help to highlight how\ntruly unusual your world is.
After that, I resumed my efforts to\nproject my consciousness here.
I believed I would find my way back\none day...and I was right.
And thus you've appeared before us\nonce again.
Yes. And my channel being severed\nis not the only peculiar thing.
There are powers besides the Other that\nare emerging here. Our older siblings act\nupon schemes of their own...
Most importantly, the Other's power\nhas entered a new, third vessel.
In all of the worlds I have visited,\nthat has never happened.
This world follows a different path,\nand it gives me hope we may yet find\na way to defeat the Other here.
...And that I will finally find a way to not\nlose everyone.
Must have been awful to have been by\nyourself for so long.
Though I have endured many dark times,\nI do not endure them alone.
I carry with me the hopes of all whose\nsacrifices brought me to this point—\nand that is why I cannot lose.
One day, I WILL free my brother from\nthe Other and save my own world!
Seriously, man? That's all you got?\nI kinda expected a response with a\nlittle more zest.
I just can't get over how very like Zethia\nshe is—and yet how different.
Heh. I know exactly how you feel.\nTo me, you are every bit my brother,\nand yet not my brother at all.
You guys are gonna break my brain.
I understand it on a logical level,\nyet it still somehow confuses me.
Which is why I would ask you all\nto refer to me as ＂Zena.＂
The princess you seek to save is Zethia,\nso it is Zena who will fight at your side.
I suppose different names make sense\nfor different people.
Indeed. So if all of you feel the same,\nit should make things a good deal\neasier for everyone involved.
Now THAT'S easy enough\nfor me to understand!
Can't say I'm a hundred percent on board,\nbuuut... Eh, what the hey. Let's do it!

...The Other poses a dire threat to
everyone, so let's work together to
save all of our worlds and all of
our futures!
Well, now that we got THAT outta the way,\nit's time for a welcome party!
Does this mean you officially\nacknowledge me as part of your team?!
Are you kidding me? You're all in!\nCouldn't have been easy to spill your\nguts like that, you know?
Thank you for putting yourself through\nthat for us. You have our gratitude.
It's all right. I must be strong.
For each world I have visited and every\npast I have relived, I must grow stronger.
Then let us get some proper\nnutrition into you.
I will make something truly special\nin your honor tonight.
Wait, hang on. She's a spiritual mana\nprojection or something, yeah?\nCan she even eat?
Is there no limit to your gluttony?
Oh man, I bet it's been a long time since\nyou've seen happy people! Sorry, but\nit's always kinda like this around here.
I actually remember this quite fondly.
(Yet I cannot help but fear\nI might lose it all anew.)

(One day, that promise will be kept:
I will transcend time, causality, and
even destiny itself to see my dear
brother once more.)
